CREATE TABLE cross_docking_delays (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  warehouse_id UUID NOT NULL,
  arrival_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  departure_time TIMESTAMP,
  delay_minutes INT,
  reason TEXT
)

arrival_date DATE,

delay_reason VARCHAR(255))
